Sec. 58.036.

PAYMENT ENFORCEABLE BY MANDAMUS.

Statute text rendered on: 8/6/2022

- 307 -

Payment of the

AGRICULTURE CODE

bonds and performance by the authority or the commissioner of its or
his functions and duties under this chapter and the Texas
Constitution may be enforced in the state supreme court by mandamus
or other appropriate proceeding.
Added by Acts 1987, 70th Leg., 2nd C.S., ch. 32, art. 2, Sec. 1, eff.
Oct. 20, 1987; Acts 1989, 71st Leg., ch. 1247, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1,
1989.

